// TEST CASE 4 — Database: SQL on Write-Heavy Scenario Raises BugRisk and Latency
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
/**
 * DESCRIPTION:
 *   Validates the conditional DB penalty for using SQL on write-heavy scenarios
