/**
 * DESCRIPTION:
 *   Validates the progressive difficulty mechanic where traffic spikes escalate
 *   each cycle:
 *     spike = round(200 × spikeFactor × (1 + cycle × 0.15))
 *   This ensures later cycles are harder, creating a meaningful game loop.
 *
 * EXPECTED BEHAVIOUR:
